            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-298c461c68dac82d-1a5495 twpub-298c461c68dac82d-02592a twpub-298c461c68dac82d-6b4cd0\"><h1><span class=\"ph2\">INCIDENTS</span><br>\n<span class=\"ph5\">IN THE</span><br>\nLIFE OF A SLAVE GIRL.</h1></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/298c461c68dac82d/text/000000013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/298c461c68dac82d/text/000000013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-298c461c68dac82d-1a5495 twpub-298c461c68dac82d-02592a twpub-298c461c68dac82d-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"ph4\">Written by Herself.</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/298c461c68dac82d/text/000000014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/298c461c68dac82d/text/000000014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-298c461c68dac82d-1a5495 twpub-298c461c68dac82d-02592a twpub-298c461c68dac82d-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"ph3\">Linda Brent</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/298c461c68dac82d/text/000000015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/298c461c68dac82d/text/000000015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-298c461c68dac82d-1a5495 twpub-298c461c68dac82d-02592a twpub-298c461c68dac82d-6b4cd0\"><p>“Northerners know nothing at all about Slavery. They think it is perpetual bondage only. They have no conception of the depth of <i>degradation</i> involved in that word, SLAVERY; if they had, they would never cease their efforts until so horrible a system was overthrown.”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/298c461c68dac82d/text/000000016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/298c461c68dac82d/text/000000016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-298c461c68dac82d-1a5495 twpub-298c461c68dac82d-02592a twpub-298c461c68dac82d-6b4cd0\"><p>A Woman Of North Carolina.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/298c461c68dac82d/text/000000017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/298c461c68dac82d/text/000000017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-298c461c68dac82d-1a5495 twpub-298c461c68dac82d-02592a twpub-298c461c68dac82d-6b4cd0\"><p>“Rise up, ye women that are at ease! Hear my voice, ye careless daughters! Give ear unto my speech.”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/298c461c68dac82d/text/000000018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/298c461c68dac82d/text/000000018",
